&lt;h2 id="windows-客户端"&gt;Windows 客户端&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://github.com/canton7/SyncTrayzor/releases/latest"target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;
 Synctrayzor
